description:
MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Yes, I am finally playing FTB, and I am very much enjoying it. I figured I would bring you guys along with me by making a few videos of what I'm up to on the server.
